---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
  
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #b8b5b5;
    }
  
    h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #c8c6c6;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #ddd;
      padding-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }
  
    p {
      margin-left: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #e5e3e3;
    }
  
    .content-section {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
</style>
<Layout>
    <h1>Terms of Pendia</h1>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Content Creation SaaS</h2>
        <p>
            The parent company oversees a state-of-the-art SaaS platform tailored for content creators. 
            This platform offers tools for video editing, graphics design, scheduling, and cross-platform publishing.
        </p>
        <p>
            Key goals include simplifying workflows, enabling collaboration, and integrating AI-driven insights 
            to optimize content performance.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Wholesale Pipeline Firm</h2>
        <p>
            This subsidiary focuses on streamlining supply chain operations for businesses. It connects wholesalers 
            and retailers through a robust digital platform, facilitating bulk transactions and offering real-time 
            inventory management.
        </p>
        <p>
            Services include logistics coordination, demand forecasting, and end-to-end supply chain transparency.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Digital Life Assisting Firm</h2>
        <p>
            Designed to enhance everyday life, this firm provides virtual assistance services powered by advanced AI. 
            Offerings range from personal finance management and smart home integration to health tracking and 
            virtual concierge services.
        </p>
        <p>
            The mission is to empower individuals by seamlessly integrating digital solutions into their daily routines.
        </p>
    </div>
</Layout>
